cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.SE. 

The paper deals with the automatic transformation of GUI screenshots into code using deep learning techniques. This involves image processing (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and code generation (cs.SE). The proposed attention-based hierarchical code generation model also involves the use of recurrent neural networks (cs.AI) and training the components in an end-to-end manner (cs.LG). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV, cs.AI, and cs.LG, followed by cs.CL and cs.SE.
